node.text:
Registration is OPEN for the annual Alpha King Challenge 🍺 

We usually crown the winner for the best hoppy beer at @rockbottombrewery in Denver during the @greatamericanbeerfestival — but this year we’ll be live streaming the competition from our brewery on October 16 with @yakimachief. Hit the link in our bio to register for the epic battle of beers ⚔️

node.text:
Our friends at the kiosk wanted to tell you that we’ll be closed on Monday for Labor Day 🍻 swing by the brewery before 7pm Sunday night + build up that holiday weekend battle box. 

→ 3floyds.com for details

node.text:
SPEED CASTLE 🏰

Previously only available on draft, Speed Castle makes it way into bottle form. A Pilsner of profound complexity and crispness, you’ll find bottles of our latest release available exclusively at our kiosk.
For more details visit 3floyds.com ⚡️

node.text: Ride out what’s left of summer with a fresh round of our foeder fermented sour peach saison 💥 Subtle notes of pear, citrus and peach candy aromas await you. Available at our kiosk + hitting stores near you.

node.text:
Today marks the return of Region X, our take on a German-style Dortmunder lager to help get everyone ready for fall around The Region. ⚡️

Region X is available starting today for a limited time exclusively at our kiosk. 

For more info visit 3floyds.com ⛓

node.text:
“He dwells on a great mountain. What use to call on him? Little he cares if men live or die. Better to be silent than to call his attention to you; he will send you dooms, not fortune!”
-    Robert E. Howard

Descending from a dark and misty mountain, Crom’s Beard has arrived for the first time in package form. ⚔️ A single hopped IPA using only Strata hops, our latest release features huge tropical and citrus notes with aromas of pineapple, mango, and grapefruit. 

We’ve also got some sick new shirts to go along with the beer, if you're into that sort of thing. 

Get the beer and gear starting today at our kiosk, and hitting all 3 Floyds markets in the coming weeks. 💥

When you taste it, something happens . . .

New beer drop - DISMEMBERS ONLY, a 13.5% barrel aged Imperial Stout with cocoa nibs, Griottines cherries, and Thai bananas. 💥

Available for a limited time, you’ll find Dismembers Only in howlers starting today exclusively at our kiosk. For more info visit 3floyds.com ⚔️

node.text: What is best in life? To crush your enemies, see them driven before you, and celebrate with a 3 Floyds beer that you bought in Michigan. ⚔️

node.text:
Cue The Pogues’ “Wild Cats of Kilkenny” . . . ☄️
 
Inspired by one of the greatest tales ever told, Daytona Stinger has arrived to take a rocket launcher to your taste buds. 💥With a light body and over-the-top notes of lime and mint, our newest release is a refreshing and mouth-watering take on the classic cocktail. Kettle soured and fermented with a mixed culture of proprietary yeasts, this sultry ale is aged on black limes, fresh and dried mint, and a healthy dose of mojito extract for a flavor and color boost.
 
Want to take it to another level? Pair it up or mix with @3floydsdistilling Blanq Reavers Rum for a taste explosion that would level even the most fortified Ferrari Daytona. ⚡️
 
Daytona Stinger is available starting today at our retail kiosk and rolling out to select 3 Floyds markets over the course of the next week.
 
Enjoy on hot summer nights and repeat after us, “Stingers pal, Stingers.” ⚔️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 3 Floyds Brewing on August 05, 2021.

node.text:
As we approach the end of summer (sigh), we all start to get a little excited for the next season and all it has to offer. You know - cooler temps, backyard fire pits, Premier League Football, ROCKTOBER, etc. 

Another thing that helps to put our favorite season over is the heralded return of Munsterfest. 🔹 Originally brewed to honor the marriage of Prince Ludwing to Princess Therese in 1810 (the very first Oktoberfest celebration), our Marzen-style Oktoberfest remains true to that brewing tradition. Showcasing balance, this fall favorite features caramel, toffee, and biscuit notes that shine in this rich, malty lager brewed with German malted barley and aromatic Bavarian noble hops. 

Munsterfest is available starting today in our kiosk and rolling out to select 3 Floyds markets now. Find out more at 3floyds.com 🍺 Es ist nicht normal.
